<p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-light dark:text-text-dark-muted text-center">
S.A. Auto Stock was founded in 2001 by Navanithananthasivam, a third-generation automotive technician from Sri Lanka. Growing up in a family of skilled car mechanics, he carried forward a passion for repairing cars and bringing honest service to every customer. Moving to British Columbia, Canada, he turned his lifelong dream into reality by opening a family-run shop known for integrity and quality workmanship.
</p>

<p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-light dark:text-text-dark-muted text-cent">
Following in his father’s footsteps, Pratheepan studied automotive technology at VCC and joined the family business, continuing the legacy. Today, S.A. Auto Stock remains a trusted name in the lower mainland, offering expert repairs for all types of vehicles, from luxury cars to everyday drivers. With fair pricing, personalized service, and dedication to customer satisfaction, the family’s passion for cars continues to drive every repair.
</p>


